**Correct Logic:** Element 29 is Copper (Cu). Element 30 is Zinc (Zn). Element 31 is Gallium (Ga). Element 32 is Germanium (Ge). Element 33 is Arsenic (As). Element 34 is Selenium (Se). Element 35 is Bromine (Br). Element 36 is Krypton (Kr). Element 37 is Rubidium (Rb). Element 38 is Strontium (Sr). Element 39 is Yttrium (Y). Element 40 is Zirconium (Zr). Element 41 is Niobium (Nb). Element 42 is Molybdenum (Mo). Element 43 is Technetium (Tc). Element 44 is Ruthenium (Ru). Element 45 is Rhodium (Rh). Element 46 is Palladium (Pd). Element 47 is Silver (Ag). Element 48 is Cadmium (Cd). Element 49 is Indium (In). Element 50 is Tin (Sn). Element 51 is Antimony (Sb). Element 52 is Tellurium (Te). Element 53 is Iodine (I). Element 54 is Xenon (Xe). Element 55 is Cesium (Cs). Element 56 is Barium (Ba). Element 57 is Lanthanum (La). Element 58 is Cerium (Ce). Element 59 is Praseodymium (Pr). Element 60 is Neodymium (Nd). Element 61 is Promethium (Pm). Element 62 is Samarium (Sm). Element 63 is Europium (Eu). Element 64 is Gadolinium (Gd). Element 65 is Terbium (Tb). Element 66 is Dysprosium (Dy). Element 67 is Holmium (Ho). Element 68 is Erbium (Er). Element 69 is Thulium (Tm). Element 70 is Ytterbium (Yb). Element 71 is Lutetium (Lu).
Okay, let's pick **Zinc** (Zn). It is the 30th element. It is named after the German word *Zink*.
**Refined Q7:** What is the chemical symbol for the element that is the 30th on the periodic table and is named after the German word for "white lead" or similar? No, *Zink* means Zinc.
**Refined Q7:** What is the chemical symbol for the element that is the 30th on the periodic table and is named after the German word *Zink*?
**Answer:** Zn.

### Q8 (Expert - Chinese)
在哪个**平**原上，1945 年发生了著名的“诺门罕战役”，这是苏日之间的一次大规模军事冲突？
**Answer:** 诺门罕平原 (Khalkhin Gol Plain). [end of text]


